data.description: Want the spaciousness of country living on 5 acres with the convenience of town? Check out this immaculate three-bedroom two bath home located within minutes of Coweta and Haskell as well as easy access to the Tulsa Metro. Interior of this home is open with the perfect amenities for a family to enjoy, including a wood-burning fireplace. The exterior has boundless opportunities for gardening, building, and raising animals.
